// Kodex Drafts
// Review and act on pending topic drafts. Shows a searchable list of drafts
// with inline diff view comparing the live topic to proposed changes.

FUNCTION ContentSection(title, draftContent, liveContent)
  Render a side-by-side comparison row for one content field.
  If draftContent differs from liveContent, show a 'Changed' badge.

---

FUNCTION Drafts()                                                       EXPORT
  CALLS: listDrafts (kodex-api), getTopic (kodex-api), approveDraft (kodex-api), rejectDraft (kodex-api)
  Read selectedProject from kodexStore.
  On mount (or project change): load all pending drafts via kodexApi.listDrafts.
  Maintain a search query; filteredDrafts matches drafts by topicName, reason, or createdBy.
  On expand (handleExpand): toggle expanded state. When expanding, fetch the live topic via
    kodexApi.getTopic to enable side-by-side comparison.
  On approve (handleApprove): call kodexApi.approveDraft then reload the draft list.
  On reject (handleReject): confirm, call kodexApi.rejectDraft, then reload.
  Render each draft with metadata, expand/approve/reject buttons, and (when expanded) a
    ContentSection comparison for conceptual, technical, files, and related fields.
